loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>博客从Blogger迁移到HUGO</title><link>https://blog.kihh.xyz/p/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E4%BB%8Eblogger%E8%BF%81%E7%A7%BB%E5%88%B0hugo/</link><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 22:37:36 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.kihh.xyz/p/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E4%BB%8Eblogger%E8%BF%81%E7%A7%BB%E5%88%B0hugo/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://resources.blog.kihh.xyz/image/20240118231417.png" alt="Featured image of post 博客从Blogger迁移到HUGO" />&lt;p>好久没有捣鼓博客了，看着原来灰土土的博客主题感觉是真的丑，但Blogger上的主题又太少了，于是决定把博客迁移到别的程序。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>我第一次搭建博客用的是HEXO，于是我就去HEXO官网的&lt;a class="link" href="https://hexo.io/themes/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Themes&lt;/a>去找主题，但找了半天都没找到自己喜欢的主题。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>我又去HUGO官网的&lt;a class="link" href="https://themes.gohugo.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Themes&lt;/a>去找主题，一眼就看到了&lt;a class="link" href="https://themes.gohugo.io/themes/hugo-theme-stack/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>这个主题&lt;/a>，简约又绚丽，就决定是它了！&lt;/p>
&lt;p>然后又捣鼓了两个小时怎么部署HUGO，跟HEXO的部署方式差不多，我用了Github Action + Cloudflare Pages的方式部署。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>现在博客已经由Blogger迁移到了HUGO，以后也会时常更新一些文章吧！&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Linux常用脚本合集</title><link>https://blog.kihh.xyz/p/linux%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/</link><pubDate>Tue, 20 Dec 2022 18:26:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.kihh.xyz/p/linux%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/</guid><description>&lt;p>1.奈飞原生检测&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-gdscript3" data-lang="gdscript3">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">wget&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">-&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">O&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">nf&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">https&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">//&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">github&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">com&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">sjlleo&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">netflix&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">-&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">verify&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">releases&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">download&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">v3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mf">1.0&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">nf&lt;/span>\&lt;span class="n">_linux&lt;/span>\&lt;span class="n">_amd64&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">chmod&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">+&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">x&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">nf&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">./&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">nf&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>2.TikTok原生检测&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">bash &amp;lt;(curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lmc999/TikTokCheck/main/tiktok.sh)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>3.BBR一键脚本&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget --no-check-certificate https://github.com/teddysun/across/raw/master/bbr.sh &amp;amp;&amp;amp; chmod +x bbr.sh &amp;amp;&amp;amp; ./bbr.sh
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>4.Cloudflare Warp一键脚本&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget -N https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fscarmen/warp/main/menu.sh &amp;amp;&amp;amp; bash menu.sh
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>5.宝塔面板7.7.0原版无登录&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget -O install.sh http://f.cccyun.cc/bt/install_6.0.sh &amp;amp;&amp;amp; bash install.sh
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>6.Bench.sh综合跑分&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget -qO- bench.sh | bash
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
